Interface CollectionChangeAware<V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - the value type.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ValueCollectionEditor<E,C>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractValueCollectionEditor, CompositeValueEditor, NameEditor, TagListComponentValueEditor, TemplateCompositeValueEditor, ValueListEditor, ValueSetEditor

    public interface CollectionChangeAware<V>
    Implementations can retrieve collection changes.

    Russ Tennant (russ@proteus.co)

      • clearCollectionChanges

        void clearCollectionChanges()
        Clear any collection changes. This is called automatically whenever ValueEditor.setValue(Object) is called.

        Get any collection changes.
